Last Broadcast Date: Thu 23 Jun 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, a young Mexican using hip hop to help gangsters build new lives for themselves. Also the Afghan midwife who's received international recognition for her work and won the respect of her village And India's sharp-shooting, medal-winning grandmother on how her community reacted when she first took up a pistol. Show less